+# Changelog
+
+All notable changes to this project are documented here.
+
+The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.1.0/),
+and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).
+
+## [0.2.0] - 2026-05-27
+
+Pre-1.0 breaking-platform migration. Under `0.x`, breaking changes increment the
+minor version.
+
+### Changed (Breaking)
+
+- **Upgraded to Next.js 16** (from 14, App Router). Requires re-running
+  `npm install`; review the Next 14→16 migration notes if you have custom config.
+- **Upgraded to React 19** (from 18). Components and any local patches should be
+  validated against the React 19 runtime.
+- **Migrated to Tailwind CSS 4** (from 3) via `@tailwindcss/postcss`. Global styles
+  now use `@import "tailwindcss"` instead of the `@tailwind base/components/utilities`
+  directives; the PostCSS pipeline replaces `tailwindcss` + `autoprefixer` with the
+  single `@tailwindcss/postcss` plugin.
+- **Upgraded to TypeScript 6** (from 5) and **ESLint 10** (from 9).
+
+### Dependencies
+
+- Bumped `@google/generative-ai` to `^0.24.1`.
+- Refreshed dev tooling: `@types/node`, `@types/react`, `@types/react-dom`,
+  `eslint-plugin-react-hooks`, `globals`, `postcss`, `autoprefixer`,
+  `typescript-eslint` updated to align with the new platform.
+
+## [0.1.0]
+
+- Initial 90-day MVP scaffold: design system, three routes
+  (`/`, `/landing-claude`, `/dashboard`), and the `/docs` build backlog.
+

